title: Lvl 30 that cant post on forums send help
body: Title is self explanatory, i want to speak about issues i'm encountering in player behavior n stuff but system isnt updating.

replies.body: Every once and awhile someone's board's profile needs a little push to make sure it updates with your Summoner level. Once you posted here, it synced up those levels and you're showing as level 30 now ^_^!
